type: software
title: 'Joanium Classic'
abstract: >
  Joanium Classic is a local-first AI desktop assistant that combines multi-model chat,
  scheduled automations, background agents, MCP server support, and native
  integrations with GitHub, Gmail, Google Drive, and more — without sending
  data to the cloud.
